<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">该平台是我省于2023年年底上线运行的公共就业招聘平台，同步上线运行江西“5+2就业之家”公共就业招聘软件。按照“实用、管用、好用”和“人找岗位便捷，岗位找人精准”的建设思路，该软件上联人社部、省政府相关信息系统，下接市、县公共就业信息平台，依托省电子政务平台、人力资源地图等信息资源，支撑全省“5+2就业之家”建设，免费为求职者和用人单位提供便捷、精准、高效的公共就业服务。高校就业之家是全省“5+2”就业之家的重要组成部分，主要为高校学生提供更加便捷化、精准化、多元化的公共就业创业服务。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">为帮助用人单位和毕业生更好使用该平台，促进深入合作，实现资源共享，现诚邀用人单位和广大毕业生注册使用江西软件职业技术大学就业之家。注册使用步骤如下：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一、企业注册流程</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.企业扫码注册登录</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717678627180016696.png" title="1717678627180016696.png" alt="image.png"/><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717678740628071135.png" title="1717678740628071135.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717678790669004525.png" title="1717678790669004525.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717678863725091630.png" title="1717678863725091630.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">二、学生注册流程</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">线上网站注册</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679036848067723.png" title="1717679036848067723.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679128403060240.png" title="1717679128403060240.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679177991083992.png" title="1717679177991083992.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">校园“5+2就业之家”（创客大厦负一楼）建设图片</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679262946005556.png" title="1717679262946005556.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679320290020683.png" title="1717679320290020683.png" alt="image.png" width="713" height="559" style="width: 713px; height: 559px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679425311099582.png" title="1717679425311099582.png" alt="image.png" width="719" height="534" style="width: 719px; height: 534px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679503668029032.png" title="1717679503668029032.png" alt="image.png" width="722" height="521" style="width: 722px; height: 521px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679634867043700.png" title="1717679634867043700.png" alt="image.png" width="725" height="503" style="width: 725px; height: 503px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240606/1717679718435011538.png" title="1717679718435011538.png" alt="image.png" width="729" height="505" style="width: 729px; height: 505px;"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">稿源：江西软件职业技术大学就创指导中心</span></p>